Package alice.tuprolog.lib

Class Summary
BasicLibrary This class defines a set of basic built-in predicates for the tuProlog engine Library/Theory dependency: none
DCGLibrary Library for managing DCGs.
EDCGLibrary Library for managing DCGs.
IOLibrary This class provides basic I/O predicates.
ISOIOLibrary This class provides basic ISO I/O predicates.
ISOLibrary This class represents a tuProlog library providing most of the built-ins predicates and functors defined by ISO standard.
JavaLibrary This class represents a tuProlog library enabling the interaction with the Java environment from tuProlog.
TheoryLibrary Library built from Prolog theory.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidObjectIdException This exception is raised when a not valid identifier is used to register an object in the JavaLibrary
